long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Insights by xs:code is a free extension that provides developers with open source repository analytics on Github. The extension analyzes data from multiple sources to help you identify if an open source component on Github is right for your project. Request patches, bug fixes and permissive licenses directly from the open source developer through our easy-to-use interface.
